pull

public void pull()
Description copied from interface: Poolable
Inform the object that it is used again. The idea is to prevent some bugs.

When a class is informed that it is pulled, it has to check if it is not allready done. If it is the case, an exception has to be thrown. This method hsa to be called by the pool
